      <hedline>
        <hl1>THE INNER LIFE</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Americans are polled on almost everything, except what they hold closest -- concerns of the heart and mind. For a special issue, The Times Magazine commissioned a poll that asked how people understand their identities. The results reveal religious beliefs and sexual mores; where people find happiness; what causes anxiety.</p>
        <p>Plus: An opportunity to respond to the poll online.</p>
      </block>
